data.description: Beautiful country home in small, quiet community.  Property is across the street from an outstanding, small school. This is a mobile home on permanent foundation with large kitchen with double ovens, warming drawer, tons of counter space and lots of cabinets.  Large island with split level provides even more possibilities.  Two beautiful fireplaces add warmth to this home.  A comfortable living room and a large 20 x 30 family room offer a great place to host family and friends.  All bedrooms have large walk in closets.  This house includes one jack and Jill full bath.  There is also a water softener installed as well as a utility sink.  The front of this home has a beautiful covered porch with Trex decking, while the back yard has a large covered deck. This property has over 50 rose bushes to add beauty during the summer with lots of trees. The roses and trees are all connected by a timer controlled watering system.
